    "testimonials_byJFpb": {
      "type": "testimonials",
      "blocks": {
        "testimonial_UPjm8b": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<h6>\"These Saved My Life!  </h6><h6>These flip flops saved my summer! My plantar fasciitis was really bad and when I put these on I felt relief almost immediately. The discomfort continues to subside more and more each day, and is still improving, which I largely attribute to wearing these all day, every day. Plus, they felt very secure even when wet. Very thankful for these!\" </h6>",
            "author": "Lisa R",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_xPKLWB": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<h6>\"My Favorite!<br/>These were the first shoe I ordered from Aetrex. I loved them immediately. I am now on my 3rd pair, including one for my daughter since she kept stealing mine! They are cushiony & supportive enough for a day at an amusement park plus the strap keeps them secure. Casual enough for everyday, but dressy enough for a night out means only packing one pair for trips.\" </h6>",
            "author": "Holly J.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        },
        "testimonial_RixBWT": {
          "type": "testimonial",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "quote",
            "text": "<h6>\"Better Than My Bare Feet! </h6><h6>These sandals are perfect. They are very cushioned and supportive in all the right places. I can already feel the difference with my pronation issues when I wear these slides. I also love that they are cute and so easy to wear. I wear them out or just around the house. I couldn't recommend more!!!\" </h6>",
            "author": "Kimberly S.",
            "author_info": "",
            "author_url": "",
            "image_ratio": "rounded",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
          }
        }
